<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 01 at 10:26PM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Heavy snow showers overnight tonight...
Heavy snow showers will move through the area overnight tonight.
Expect brief bursts of heavy snow, which will reduce visibility
to under a half mile at times and a quick coating to a half inch
of snow with these snow showers. Roads may quickly become snow
covered and slick, so please use caution if traveling tonight.</description>
